data.description: **Price Reduction** AS-IS - Come and get a taste of Petworth living.  You'll love this classic brick row house in the heart of DC.  Upon entering, your new  home has an immense  living room off to the right.  A gorgeous stone accent wall with a beautiful remote-controlled electric fireplace with multicolor flames sits in the middle of the living room, ready for you to get cozy.  An open concept provides a spacious dining room which flows effortlessly into the kitchen area.  The beautiful center waterfall island with gorgeous white quartz counter top is an excellent accent to the charming custom white cabinets.  High-end black stainless steel Kitchen Aid appliances with a built-in convectional microwave oven, sits within a custom pantry, tops of the kitchen appeal.  Rich, dark original hardwood floors continue seamlessly throughout the first and second levels.  An artistic custom panel wall along the main stairway sets this house apart from the typical rowhouse .  The second floor has three (3) well proportioned bedrooms with one  full bathroom in hallway, featuring classic marble floors.  The Master bedroom offers a newly installed full bathroom with classic marble floors.  The fully finished basement offers a living room space, laundry area with washer and dryer and a half bathroom.  This home also has a large spacious backyard which includes a one car garage.  This charming home also has recently installed central a/c and new windows throughout.
